_sText: This is a remake of the original scoutzknivez map.  It is simply an edited version that i spent some time on to open it up a lil.  I added a bunker and better strafing surfaces with a few extra jumps.  The SS in the name can be found on all my maps and it represents me (mapper: SinistrSausage) not my clan (SiNiStRSyNdICaTE).  Any recommendations or questions just ask!!  Enjoy!
